snippet.title: Hi-Fi RUSH | PS5 Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Grab your guitar and go from wannabe to rockstar in Tango Gameworks' award-winning rhythm action game Hi-Fi RUSH, available today on PlayStation 5!

Fight back against the machinations of an evil robotics megacorporation as Chai, an aspiring rocker whose music-player-for-a-heart makes everything moves to the beat!

The PlayStation 5 version includes the Arcade Challenge! Update!, with two bonus modes that will put your musical robot powers to the test! 

Read more at hifirush.com, and follow us on X at @hifiRush! 

ESRB RATING: Teen with Fantasy Violence and Language
